            "width": 2500,
            "height": 1875,
            "credit": "",
            "caption": "<p>After warm weather and little snowfall, snow remains mostly on north-tilted slopes and in cross-loaded features. Isolated areas of firm snow on very steep slopes are the most likely place you may trigger a small slide.</p>",
